Package: scto
Type: Package
Title: Modern and Seamless 'SurveyCTO' Data Pipelines
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2025-12-29
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Gutama Girja", "Urago",
      email = "girjagutama@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5588-2301")
    )
  )
Description: An R client for the 'SurveyCTO' REST API that provides a modern, 
    consistent interface for programmatically accessing server resources. 
    Built on top of the 'httr2' package, it enables secure and efficient retrieval 
    of data and tidying to return analysis-ready data. In addition, it generates clean variable and 
    value labels for 'Stata' users. The package includes functions to download 
    form metadata, form definitions, attachments, and associated media files. 
    It emphasizes robust authentication and request handling, making it 
    suitable for automated survey monitoring and downstream analysis.
